fulltitle: Roy Hargrove: Bradley's, Frank Foster, And What Young Cats Should Remember
description:
Jazz bassist Jonah Jonathan interviews grammy award winning trumpeter Roy Hargrove for his series: The Jazz Musician's Voice.  This interview was originally shot in June 2011. Roy passed away in 2018.
Thanks for watching and please subscribe to us and give a like button. Subscribing really helps us out because you are notified when new videos come out. Share this video on social media if you enjoy it because it helps keep jazz alive. Thank you!
